                                        {description || (isVietnamese 
                                            ? "─Éß║╖c sß║ún ch├¡nh gß╗æc Viß╗çt Nam, ─æ╞░ß╗úc tuyß╗ân chß╗ìn kß╗╣ l╞░ß╗íng v├á ─æ├│ng g├│i theo ti├¬u chuß║⌐n khß║»t khe ─æß╗â giß╗» trß╗ìn vß║╣n h╞░╞íng vß╗ï truyß╗ün thß╗æng. Sß║ún phß║⌐m hiß╗çn ─æang c├│ sß║╡n tß║íi c├íc kho h├áng cß╗ºa LIKEFOOD tß║íi Mß╗╣."
                                            : "Authentic Vietnamese specialty, carefully selected and packaged to preserve traditional flavors. Products are available at LIKEFOOD warehouses in the USA.")}
                                    </p>
                                </div>

